  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <lg xml:id="TolC398">
        <l>evvayiṉ viṉaiyu mavviya ṉilaiyum.</l>
      </lg>
    </body>
  </text>

  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Iḷampūraṇar</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Namaccivāya Mutaliyār</persName> 1931, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZMelJhy.TVA_BOK_0007521/page/211/mode/1up">211</ref>–<ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZMelJhy.TVA_BOK_0007521/page/212/mode/1up">212</ref>.</p>
<p>iccūttiram eṉnutaliṟṟō veṉiṉ, itu muṟṟuc colloḻittu oḻinta peyarecca viṉaiyeccaṅkaṭku āvatōr ilakkaṇam uṇarttutal nutaliṟṟu.</p>
<p>urai : mēṟ kūṟappaṭṭa muṟṟuccollē yaṉṟip peyareccamum viṉaiyeccamum mūṉṟukālamum mūṉṟiṭamum uṭaiyavāy viṉaiyum viṉaikkuṟippumpaṟṟi varum eṉpāṉ, 'evvayiṉ viṉaiyum avviyaṉilaiyum' eṉṟār eṉpatu.</p>
<p>maṟṟu,</p>
<lg xml:id="TolC428-Iḷam-cit1">
<l>'viṉaiyeṉap paṭuvatu vēṟṟumai koḷḷātu</l>
<l>niṉaiyuṅ kālaik kālamoṭu tōṉṟum'</l></lg>	<p>(tol. viṉai-1)</p>
<p>eṉpuḻi, ellā viṉaiccollum mūṉṟu kālattiṟkum uriya eṉappaṭṭatu.</p>
<p>iṉi,</p>
<lg xml:id="TolC428-Iḷam-cit2">
<l>'eñciya kiḷavi yiṭattoṭu civaṇi</l>
<l>yaimpāṟku muriya'</l></lg>	<p>(tol. viṉai - 26)</p>
<p>eṉpuḻi, evviṭattiṟkum urimaiyuṅ kūṟappaṭṭatu piṟaveṉiṉ, mēl aṅṅaṉaṅ kūṟiṉārēṉum, atu vilakkuppaṭṭatu ; īṇṭup pōtantu muṟṟuc collaiyē vitantu mūṉṟiṭattiṟkum uriya eṉṟamaiyāṉ, atu nōkki yīṇṭu itu kūṟiṉār eṉpatu.	(32)</p>
    </body>
  </text>

